---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ContactBanner from '../components/ContactBanner.astro';
---

<Layout title="Software e Integración | Gravocom">
  <section class="relative bg-slate-950 py-24 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10" style="background-image: radial-gradient(#F97316 0.5px, transparent 0.5px); background-size: 30px 30px;"></div>
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-orange-500/10 border border-orange-500/20 px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-6">
        <span class="text-orange-500 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em]">Smart Integration</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white uppercase tracking-tighter mb-6">
        Software de <span class="text-orange-500 italic">Control y Diseño</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Interfaces potentes diseñadas para el marcado de precisión, automatización de trazabilidad y compatibilidad total con flujos de trabajo industriales.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        
        <div class="group p-8 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl hover:border-orange-500 hover:bg-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-slate-900 text-orange-500 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-tight mb-4">Trazabilidad Avanzada</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Generación automática de códigos **1D y 2D (QR, Data Matrix)** vinculados dinámicamente a sus bases de datos y procesos de producción.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6 flex gap-2">
            <span class="text-[9px] font-bold px-2 py-1 bg-slate-200 rounded text-slate-500 uppercase">Excel/SQL</span>
            <span class="text-[9px] font-bold px-2 py-1 bg-slate-200 rounded text-slate-500 uppercase">Dynamic QR</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group p-8 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl hover:border-orange-500 hover:bg-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-slate-900 text-orange-500 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-tight mb-4">Compatibilidad Total</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Soporte nativo para archivos vectoriales **AI, DXF, PLT** y formatos de imagen. Importación fluida para grabados técnicos de alta complejidad.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6 flex gap-2">
            <span class="text-[9px] font-bold px-2 py-1 bg-slate-200 rounded text-slate-500 uppercase">Vector Support</span>
            <span class="text-[9px] font-bold px-2 py-1 bg-slate-200 rounded text-slate-500 uppercase">CAD/CAM</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group p-8 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl hover:border-orange-500 hover:bg-white transition-all duration-300 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-slate-900 text-orange-500 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-tight mb-4">Asesoría en Programas</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Desarrollo de scripts y aplicaciones a medida para optimizar tiempos de grabado, automatizar secuencias y asegurar el control de calidad.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6 flex gap-2">
            <span class="text-[9px] font-bold px-2 py-1 bg-orange-100 rounded text-orange-600 uppercase">Custom Scripts</span>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="relative bg-slate-950 rounded-[2rem] p-10 md:p-16 overflow-hidden border-b-8 border-orange-500 shadow-2xl">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-orange-500/10 blur-[100px]"></div>
        
        <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-10">
          <div class="text-center md:text-left">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white uppercase tracking-tighter mb-4">
              ¿Problemas con tu <span class="text-orange-500">configuración?</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-md text-lg">
              Brindamos soporte técnico local y capacitación remota para el uso seguro y eficiente de nuestros programas.
            </p>
          </div>
          <a href="/contacto" class="bg-orange-500 hover:bg-orange-600 text-white font-black px-10 py-5 rounded-xl uppercase tracking-widest transition-all shadow-lg shadow-orange-500/20 whitespace-nowrap">
            Hablar con Soporte
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <ContactBanner />
</Layout>